Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:04.46,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:06.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑一人之力解決了這麼多蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:08.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個厲害角色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:09.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:40.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有能出戰的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:51.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武家巡邏組 無法再繼續履行職責了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:53.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.09,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾上大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:57.81,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就交給鄙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:04.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已誇下海口要守衛江戶安全 卻落此窩囊地步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:19.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島 在你回來之前 我會讓你看看武家組的強韌的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 要盡快前去增援
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:30.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【與父親的修行！富岳三十六劍 ！！】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您快走吧 吉宗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:45.75,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此等小事 何須如此驚慌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:47.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉宗大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:53.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這只不過是個預告罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:59.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西邊 還有一場惡戰在等待著我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:01.86,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.62,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬萬不可啊 家重大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:08.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去援助我的摯友仁兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:10.43,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:14.04,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是家重大人 您有學過劍術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:14.81,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一竅不通！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:16.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連切水果都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未有過！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:21.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我有豐富的理論知識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:25.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說劍術原本發祥於名為東國七流的流派
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:29.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由七名神官從東國中心發揚光大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:34.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要借這些知識 替那傢伙守護住他的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在仁兵衛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:39.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月島…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.72,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:46.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:47.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救救大姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:05.67,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常住戰陣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.49,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春小姐 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:17.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛大人 我就知道您一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:18.85,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.77,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:32.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼龐大的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:38.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑一人之力解決了這麼多蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:40.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個厲害角色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑一人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:55.63,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來無恙啊 仁兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.06,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父親大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.06,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:09.61,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹部空門正對敵人 你這個蠢兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:16.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修行還遠遠不夠  身為武士 應常住戰陣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:19.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時都要如身臨戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謹遵父親教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:27.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 讓我來看看你長進了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:29.30,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:41.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 為順利完成八丈島任務及成功守住江戶 乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:43.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:48.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我也跟著沾光 真是慚愧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:50.66,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在說什麼呢 源十郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:55.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場祝捷大會能夠召開 您可是功不可沒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:06:02.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來我是不想與身份低賤者對酌的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:06.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 源十郎大人當真好本領呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:10.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真教人甘拜下風  有機會請務必與在下切磋一番
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:14.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請也跟在下切磋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:19.17,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爹真有人氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟好久不見 沒什麼要講的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:25.67,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必 我們已經用劍充分交談過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.65,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼用劍交談…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.09,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你單方面被揍而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:34.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們平時就是那樣交談的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你家裏…真夠嗆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:41.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 在八丈島上到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:43.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:47.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很遺憾 幾乎都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:49.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:02.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 關於仁兵衛君的變貌我們會調查的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心不要說漏了嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:11.91,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下只記得跟蟲狩打鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:15.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有跟蟲奉行大人的侍女小姐相見的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侍女小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:19.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 蟲奉行大人現在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:23.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下有事一定要見他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.09,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:29.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你我的身份 怎麼可能見得到她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:32.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見不到？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:36.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~仁兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長福丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:41.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 我好想你?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:47.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:50.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:53.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江戶真是個好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:54.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:58.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛 你在這兒都學到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:01.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開家也有段時間了 說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一件重要的事就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識到了自己的弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:12.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從來到江戶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:16.59,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因自己沒出息 總是受助於他人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:23.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在八丈島也一定…吃了敗戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:28.88,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身負保護蟲奉行大人 守衛江戶的重任…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:31.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 我辜負了您的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:34.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我…就因為我的弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:38.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給父親開創的「月島流」劍術抹了黑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:43.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是 萬分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:50.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛啊 我可從來不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何時准許過你自稱「月島流」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:57.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有多少斤兩我還不知道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:03.73,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是個半吊子 竟想著背負「月島流」這個名號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子未免太猖狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:08.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:10.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:12.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從明天開始 踏上修行之路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島變化的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:25.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是因為把我的頭髮含於口中所致
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:31.39,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 普通人是不可能發生如此變樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開門見山地說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:40.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和你一樣是蟲狩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒義務告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:47.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 請保重貴體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:53.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟現在的你手無縛雞之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:13.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  此處竟是這等冷清之所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:18.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在月島在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:38.72,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島 是你讓我想起我也是人類之軀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:42.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我卻沒能告訴你我的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.12,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還懷疑你是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:49.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我說一聲對不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:51.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這願望若能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:55.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕此後再也無法從那裏出來也無悔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:06.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月 月島
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:14.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春小姐 多謝你送來的慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:15.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:26.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛大人 明天開始就要踏上修行之旅了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是早點歇息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:33.29,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 為了江戶 為了蟲奉行大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:35.63,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下一定要抓緊練習 讓自己變強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽公公 早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:50.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:51.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:52.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:59.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過這次修行 我一定要變強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:02.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊遍富士五湖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.81,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:07.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在富士樹海收集食物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.35,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去攀登富士山的山頂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:13.06,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:19.65,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始 我要將月島流的秘技傳授於你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:24.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該…該不會是教我富岳三十六劍吧 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:26.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶天吶 終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 富岳三十六劍就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:37.91,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人年輕之時嘔心瀝血領悟出的三十六式刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:42.73,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中包括能一刀劈開大海的絕技
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:46.85,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搶你老爹的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:51.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期限是向松之原小鳥大人請的這三天假
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:55.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這三天內你需將三十六招式全部學會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:57.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全…全部的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:59.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那個時候 仁兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:04.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就可以堂堂正正地使用月島流的名號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:08.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:16.27,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:19.75,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你接下來要學的富岳招式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:30.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島流 富岳鐵錘斬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:36.08,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是砍 卻如同錘擊般獨特的斬擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:39.80,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人的拿手絕招 富岳鐵錘斬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:46.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要涌上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:47.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:58.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 莫非您讓富士山爆發了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 仁兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:06.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏使出富岳鐵錘斬 以阻止富士山爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:09.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.65,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這裏的岩石施加重擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:14.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所產生的壓力可以阻止火山爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:19.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按這個速度 三天後岩漿就會溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:23.86,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 如果在那之前你還沒學會鐵錘斬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.73,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山腳下人們居住的村落就會被燒燬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶 這是不是有失妥當 父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:34.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我學會這個招式用了五年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:35.91,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:38.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如今可沒時間讓你磨磨蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.35,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父親大人 真是太偉大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:47.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人您特意為我創造苛刻的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:50.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了全面激發我的潛力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:52.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:57.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定不會辜負您的期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富岳鐵錘斬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心切開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:37.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:43.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整整兩天不眠不休 不吃不喝 修煉到倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.46,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子不愧是繼承了你的血統啊 悟性極高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你唱唱葉的「搖籃曲」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:08.12,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱聞此為神中神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:15.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太秦打懲常世神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.45,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.76,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍睡了一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連標記的岩石都被淹沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你要怎麼辦呢 仁兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:40.39,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩漿可不等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:43.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會大概還有一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:02.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果失敗了 山腳下的人們就會有性命之虞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:09.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的奧義都在父親大人的教誨中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:12.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為武士 就該常住戰陣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:15.92,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時何地都要如身臨戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:21.61,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.38,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始就是戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:30.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出陣 月島 仁兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:41.38,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要一擊即中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.55,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後變得更加強大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:52.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護江戶民眾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:56.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了有一天能兌現那個諾言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得更加強大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:03.26,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島流 富岳鐵錘斬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:09.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰場的敵人 不僅是要砍倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.75,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要徹底打敗他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:20.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:24.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做到了 終於完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.67,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看仔細了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:30.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:32.88,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富岳山嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:50.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本應該是你接下來要學的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.85,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:55.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:58.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我仁兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:01.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會盡快學會剛剛所見的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:04.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓刀法日漸精進
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.77,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你就要踏上修行的旅途了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:23.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如早點歇息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:27.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 為了江戶 為了蟲奉行大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:29.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下要抓緊時間練習 讓自己變強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:35.29,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說因為身份和地位的懸殊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:38.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下與蟲奉行大人 是不可能輕易相見的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:45.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓他人知道 我與月島私下碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:49.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕會給他帶來麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:53.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份和地位都相差太懸殊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:59.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 總有一天在下會與蟲奉行大人見面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:01.75,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變得更加強大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:05.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為那個能夠面見蟲奉行大人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:11.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在下已經與侍女小姐約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:15.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要與大家一起仰望江戶的藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲奉行大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:37.76,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待著那一刻的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:04.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等神聖莊嚴的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:09.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德川幕府的蠢貨們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:12.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的時代將在下一個冬天終結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.66,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你來打頭陣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:19.39,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿飛 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:22.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲奉行所在哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:01.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天吶
