Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:21.05,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}摯友啊 摯友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:23.59,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了令人憂傷的純粹簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:26.89,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在夕陽西下時的道場一角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:29.67,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}揮灑著汗水練習刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:33.08,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}摯友啊 摯友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:35.64,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了引人發笑的滿腔熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:39.02,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「我也是有夢想的啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:41.86,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}像傻瓜般這樣大聲叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:46.27,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:49.17,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}朝陽東昇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.79,0:00:52.14,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你會在喧鬧的街上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:55.04,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}拚命奔跑著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:58.17,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:00.99,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}深夜降臨的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:04.13,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你會穿過寬闊的大道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:06.03,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在河灘邊訴說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:09.71,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是這樣吧 我的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:16.58,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}摯友啊 摯友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.23,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了一顆赤子之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:22.28,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你正守護著重要的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:25.43,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}臉上透露著決心吧
